<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>We Received Your Message - KTBlog</title>
  <!--[if mso]>
  <noscript>
    <xml>
      <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
      </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
    </xml>
  </noscript>
  <![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f6f9;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f4f6f9;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #1E4DB7; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff;">KTBlog</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <!-- Success Icon -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <div style="display: inline-block; background-color: #ecfdf5; border: 2px solid #10b981; border-radius: 50%; width: 60px; height: 60px; line-height: 60px; text-align: center; font-size: 28px; color: #10b981;">
                      &#10003;
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 22px; color: #1a1a2e; text-align: center;">Thank You for Contacting Us!</h2>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">Hello {{name}},</p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;">We've received your message and appreciate you taking the time to reach out. Our team will review your inquiry and get back to you as soon as possible.</p>

              <!-- Info Box -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #1E4DB7; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #1e3a5f; font-size: 14px;"><strong>What happens next?</strong><br>Our team typically responds within 24-48 business hours. For urgent matters, please don't hesitate to contact us directly.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Message Summary -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f8f9fb; border-radius: 8px; margin: 24px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 24px;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; color: #1a1a2e;">Your Message Summary</h3>
                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">
                          <p style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600;">Subject</p>
                          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563;">{{subject}}</p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 12px 0 0;">
                          <p style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600;">Message</p>
                          <div style="margin-top: 4px; padding: 12px; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; white-space: pre-wrap;">{{message}}</div>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">If you need to add any additional information to your inquiry, simply reply to this email.</p>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">Thank you for your interest in KTBlog!</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a2e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">The KTBlog Team</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">&copy; {{year}} KTBlog. All rights reserved.</p>
              <p style="margin: 0; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #1E4DB7; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
